A smart way to compare each Medicare plan is to focus on a few practical questions. Does the plan include your drugs? Are your doctors in the network providers list? What are the copays, limits, and annual limit on referrals? You should also compare Medicare Advantage with Original Medicare plus a drug plan and possible supplemental coverage.

